1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:37,920
=Episode 18=

3
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,790
Jing,

4
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:40,719
I think maybe

5
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,829
you should take
your husband to the hospital.

6
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:43,589
Well,

7
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:44,879
getting some medicine

8
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,880
to help regulate things would be good.

9
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,600
Forget it.

10
00:01:49,670 --> 00:01:50,880
Look...

11
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,910
Fei is about to get out of class.

12
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,949
I will go pick her up.

13
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,350
I will go with you.

14
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,880
What are you going for?

15
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,960
Let Fei come home with me today.

16
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,350
When you get home tonight,

17
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:10,110
cook a few dishes for your husband.

18
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,399
Have a couple of drinks together.

19
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,309
Remember,

20
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,629
dim the lights.

21
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:15,230
Ideally,

22
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,440
light some scented candles too.

23
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,959
Once the atmosphere is there,

24
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,560
things will naturally follow.

25
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:25,189
You can't wait,

26
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,679
right?

27
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,280
You are overthinking it.

28
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,230
Look at how happy you are.

29
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:44,510
Ms. Lu.

30
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,560
Ms. Lu.

31
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,910
Ms. Qin.

32
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,629
Let me, let me.

33
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:53,880
I will push you over.

34
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,320
This is fine, thank you.

35
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:06,189
How is your case going?
Has the hearing started?

36
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,350
Yes.

37
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,070
My brothers

38
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:11,589
forced them to do
an autopsy on my father.

39
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,789
Who is the judge?

40
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:14,320
I think

41
00:03:14,350 --> 00:03:15,469
the last name is Shu.

42
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,630
Shu Jing.

43
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,559
Judge Shu Jing is very kind.

44
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,349
Do not worry.

45
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:20,749
She will not let your two brothers

46
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:22,200
take advantage of you.

47
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,239
You came all this way

48
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,279
in this condition.

49
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,879
It must be inconvenient to take the bus.

50
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,320
Let me call you a car.

51
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:30,879
It's okay.

52
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,749
I live very close to here.

53
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,560
Just past three intersections
and I am there.

54
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:37,629
I have been walking around here often lately,
so I am already very familiar with it.

55
00:03:37,630 --> 00:03:38,880
Thank you.

56
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,029
Thank you, Ms. Qin.

57
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,720
Let me treat you to dinner.

58
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,999
It's alright.

59
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,600
Look, I already bought groceries.

60
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,349
Thank you.

61
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:48,839
It is very close. It just so happens
I have no one to eat with.

62
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,189
Come eat with me.

63
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:50,679
No, really...

64
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:53,390
You do not trust me
to treat you to a meal? Come on.

65
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,509
Then...

66
00:03:54,510 --> 00:03:56,830
Let's go eat something good.

67
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,110
Your meal is served. Please enjoy.

68
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,159
Thank you.

69
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,069
Ms. Lu, you're welcome.

70
00:04:10,070 --> 00:04:11,950
Are you used to the food here?

71
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:14,439
I am. It is delicious.

72
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,999
I did not think much of it just now,

73
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,799
but this happens

74
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,949
to be the restaurant

75
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:20,560
where I often met clients before.

76
00:04:21,150 --> 00:04:22,440
Ms. Qin,

77
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:25,030
do you think

78
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,630
I can win this case?

79
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,559
Do not worry.

80
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,070
You will definitely

81
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:34,200
win this case.

82
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,119
Think about it.

83
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,309
All these years,

84
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,510
you were the one who took care
of your father the most.

85
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,880
And your own health
is not good to begin with.

86
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,829
Doing laundry, cooking,

87
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,149
even handling his toileting needs,

88
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:45,630
not to mention
taking him to the hospital,

89
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,479
carrying him up and down,
through wind and rain,

90
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,879
all of it depended on you alone.

91
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,390
That is not easy.

92
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,709
Your two brothers

93
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:53,440
are really inconsiderate.

94
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,150
And now they are even suing you.

95
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,590
Where is their humanity?

96
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,950
No matter what,

97
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,239
my father died

98
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,760
because I

99
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,710
took him out.

100
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:13,039
I just cannot get over this in my heart.

101
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,630
I really cannot.

102
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,320
The forensic examination

103
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:19,830
will help restore the truth.

104
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,679
May I know,

105
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:28,630
what is this examination process like?

106
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:31,360
I am a little scared.

107
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,999
I do not know the exact details,

108
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,919
but I have a friend

109
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,000
who specializes in this.

110
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,080
She works at Qingcheng District
Forensic Identification Center.

111
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,309
I will ask her for you.

112
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:41,270
The institution we are going to

113
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:43,390
is the one in Qingcheng District.

114
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,510
The one on Heping Road?

115
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,590
Yes.

116
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,799
That is great.

117
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,239
I will go with you.

118
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:51,359
I cannot afford a lawyer as good as you.

119
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,709
I will not charge you.

120
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:54,119
It is just a small favor.

121
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,309
I told you

122
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,440
my friend works there, right?

123
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,360
I will just treat it as getting
a free meal from her later.

124
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,120
I'll even get a full benefit out of it.

125
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,949
Eat the noodles while they are hot.

126
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,950
They will not taste good
once they get cold.

127
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,799
Welcome back, Le.

128
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,150
Dad, Mom.

129
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,920
Look who is here.

130
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,470
Fei is here.

131
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:35,679
Come, sit.

132
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,269
Fei.

133
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,389
Come, sit.

134
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:40,119
I will get you some slippers.

135
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,950
Stretch your feet.

136
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,830
That is more comfortable. Here.

137
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,119
Take off your shoes.

138
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,709
Alright. Put your schoolbag down
and come with me.

139
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:48,069
I will pour some water for her.

140
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,629
Come with me.

141
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:48,919
Okay.

142
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:51,030
Come sit here.

143
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,359
Go take the things out.

144
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,760
Yes.

145
00:06:54,710 --> 00:06:56,559
Xiao Bing, where are my slippers?

146
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,830
I will get them for you in a bit.

147
00:06:58,830 --> 00:06:59,829
Coming.

148
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:01,069
Look.

149
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,710
Look at all my treasures.

150
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:03,999
Look.

151
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,679
Dad,

152
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,039
you even kept

153
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,069
my childhood stuff.

154
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,069
Of course.

155
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:10,120
We are saving them for our grandchild.

156
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,919
Fei, you must be thirsty.
Have some water first.

157
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,200
Have some water first.

158
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,599
What do you like?

159
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,189
- Have a sip of water first.
- Go get the slippers.

160
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:18,709
Have some water.

161
00:07:18,710 --> 00:07:20,679
Dad, Mom, Jing has something
to handle at home today,

162
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,510
so Fei will stay over
at our place tonight.

163
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:26,030
- That is great.
- That is great.

164
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,120
Fei, you can sleep with me tonight.

165
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:29,390
See?

166
00:07:30,650 --> 00:07:32,030
- That is wonderful.
- Change your shoes.

167
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,560
Do you like this?

168
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:38,069
Look at this little car.

169
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,069
Look at this car.

170
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:41,509
She still has homework
to do later, Dad, Mom.

171
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,829
Homework is important, but we also
need a balance between work and rest.

172
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,360
Let her play first.

173
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,799
Le,

174
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,069
you come play too.

175
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,039
I heard

176
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,680
that playing with toys lifts the mood.

177
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:55,240
More importantly,
it helps with brain development.

178
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,590
I...

179
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,949
Just leave them be.

180
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:59,359
Fei does not come often.

181
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,560
Let them enjoy some family time.

182
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,320
As for us,

183
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:16,560
how long has it been
since we went on a date?

184
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,000
Before we got married,

185
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:24,440
we went on dates quite often, right?

186
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:26,150
After we got married...

187
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:31,030
After we got married,
it really has not been very many times.

188
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,950
The wedding

189
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:40,590
feels like it was many years ago.

190
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,320
I can barely remember it.

191
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,950
I remember the wedding clearly.

192
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,359
Halfway through the ceremony,

193
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,599
Liu Ren

194
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,520
was stirring things up on the spot.

195
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,560
I remember.

196
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:56,350
They asked me to dance back then.

197
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:58,719
I hate dancing the most.

198
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,119
I was so nervous.

199
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,319
You grabbed the microphone

200
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,950
and said you would protect me.

201
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:05,710
At that moment, I thought,

202
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,710
"This is someone I can marry,

203
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,680
he's really so good to me."

204
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,599
What are you talking about?

205
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,359
I was drunk at the time.

206
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,160
I have never danced on stage before.

207
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,269
I had no idea

208
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,999
what I was even doing.

209
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,119
Afterward, when I watched

210
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,830
the wedding video,

211
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,909
what dancing was that?

212
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:26,160
It was chaos.

213
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,199
Yes, I remember.

214
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,800
You danced like a monkey back then.

215
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,429
Do not think I did not notice.

216
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:34,750
You even practiced in secret afterward.

217
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,440
You knew about that too?

218
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,200
You have always been like this,

219
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,920
never telling me things,

220
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,950
always making me guess.

221
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,999
When I guess wrong,

222
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,750
you say I do not understand you.

223
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,839
I really did not

224
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,520
hide things from you on purpose.

225
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,239
Think about it,

226
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,119
you are already so busy at work,

227
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,719
with so many matters
at the court every day.

228
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,669
When you come home,

229
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:03,320
how can I trouble you

230
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,710
with those little things?

231
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,549
If I do not worry about you,

232
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,640
then why did we get married?

233
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,830
Did you forget?

234
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:14,400
Back when we got married,

235
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:16,230
did we not agree

236
00:10:16,430 --> 00:10:18,440
to be honest with each other?

237
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:22,110
Have you forgotten all of that?

238
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:24,110
So all that

239
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,629
was just you brushing me off?

240
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:26,920
No.

241
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,400
I meant it.

242
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,870
I truly meant it.

243
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,830
Speaking of which,

244
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:41,400
did you ever learn the dance?

245
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,029
No.

246
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,950
But I did practice seriously.

247
00:10:46,430 --> 00:10:49,440
Besides, I never
had a chance to show it.

248
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,839
No time like the present.

249
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,950
Right now.

250
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,990
You really want to see it?

251
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:58,470
Alright.

252
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:00,509
It has been a long time.

253
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:01,079
Look,

254
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,629
I will just do the first move.

255
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:03,950
Ready, go.

256
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,710
You still look like a monkey.

257
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:14,839
Come, I will teach you.

258
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,509
I cannot dance.

259
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,199
Come on.

260
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,719
I really cannot dance.
It is very simple.

261
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,029
I have no coordination.

262
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,320
Watch carefully. Here.

263
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:37,959
Again.

264
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,110
Turn around.

265
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,560
Spin, spin.

266
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,200
Shu Jing,

267
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:01,830
having you by my side is really nice.

268
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:16,520
(Ms. Wei)

269
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,440
Ignore it.

270
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:24,200
No, I should take this.

271
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,580
Hello.

272
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,950
Do not worry.

273
00:12:34,430 --> 00:12:36,110
What is the client's request?

274
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:38,950
Okay.

275
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,440
I got it. Go ahead.

276
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:47,640
(Following He Xiuguang)

277
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,999
People who live here

278
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,909
can come down for a walk every day.

279
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:35,990
Quiet within the bustle,

280
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,920
a perfect place to settle down.

281
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:41,800
Yongxu, come take a look.

282
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,789
Distant mountains like ink,

283
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:45,440
nearby waters veiled in mist.

284
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,200
Autumn grass and withered lotus,

285
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:50,800
rippling under the sunlight.

286
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:53,950
This is a paradise on earth.

287
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,429
As we walked here just now,

288
00:14:57,430 --> 00:14:59,870
those grand buildings

289
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:02,119
were hidden among the lush greenery.

290
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:04,160
The liveliness of daily life

291
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:07,710
blends perfectly
with this natural beauty.

292
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,239
Wonderful.

293
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,269
Xiuguang,

294
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:12,830
you chose this place very well.

295
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:15,719
It seems heaven

296
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,520
is looking out for us.

297
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:22,599
If we could build a home here,

298
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:26,560
it would truly be a joy in life.

299
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:45,429
Walking barefoot

300
00:15:45,430 --> 00:15:46,599
on this kind of path

301
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,549
is very good
for the foot reflexology points.

302
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,750
Slow down.

303
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:57,470
This way.

304
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:09,909
The park next to our home

305
00:16:09,910 --> 00:16:11,520
is quite lively.

306
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:13,830
Seeing these children

307
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:17,470
reminds me of when I
used to bring Xiezhi here.

308
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,429
Dad,

309
00:16:19,430 --> 00:16:21,680
you really have a great memory.

310
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,749
I still remember when he was little,

311
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:25,629
he kept saying he wanted to be a doctor,

312
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:27,629
using a paper cup as a stethoscope,

313
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:30,520
going around listening
to the trees' heartbeats.

314
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,669
Grandpa,

315
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:38,789
you take a walk first.

316
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:40,200
I will come find you later.

317
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,990
Alright, go ahead.

318
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,479
This child.

319
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,269
Dad,

320
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:49,560
let us take a walk by the lake.

321
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:55,400
You are where I belong
for the rest of my life.

322
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:58,710
I wish I could become your belt,

323
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:01,320
wrapping around
your slender waist every day,

324
00:17:01,430 --> 00:17:03,350
following you wherever you go.

325
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:06,519
I would be your sash,

326
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:09,920
embracing your graceful form.

327
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:12,680
You truly are my soulmate.

328
00:17:20,670 --> 00:17:21,599
What are you doing?

329
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:22,949
Do not do this.

330
00:17:22,950 --> 00:17:24,550
No, do not do this.

331
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:29,270
I am sorry.

332
00:17:29,430 --> 00:17:30,710
No,

333
00:17:31,630 --> 00:17:33,360
I am the one who should apologize.

334
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:35,990
Yongxu,

335
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:38,230
I am truly sorry.

336
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,880
My passion

337
00:17:42,390 --> 00:17:44,799
was stirred by the fragrance
of these flowers and grass.

338
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,319
My soul

339
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:48,400
was cleansed by the gentle breeze here.

340
00:17:48,910 --> 00:17:51,429
Everything between you
and me converges here.

341
00:17:51,430 --> 00:17:53,080
In this perfect moment,

342
00:17:53,120 --> 00:17:55,559
in this beautiful time,

343
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:57,319
right now,

344
00:17:57,320 --> 00:17:58,640
I truly

345
00:17:58,950 --> 00:18:00,629
cannot hold back my feelings.

346
00:18:00,630 --> 00:18:01,799
But I cannot give you

347
00:18:01,800 --> 00:18:03,469
a proper embrace,

348
00:18:03,470 --> 00:18:04,359
nor can I share with you

349
00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:06,710
a life of two people,
three meals, four seasons.

350
00:18:07,190 --> 00:18:08,950
I am useless.

351
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:12,440
Xiuguang,

352
00:18:18,390 --> 00:18:20,680
how much is this place per square meter?

353
00:18:26,630 --> 00:18:28,120
Who is that?

354
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:29,710
Stop right there!

355
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:32,669
Give it back to me!

356
00:18:32,670 --> 00:18:33,879
That is my phone.

357
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:35,879
You are awful, give it back to me!

358
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:38,359
I had a bad feeling early this morning,

359
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:40,440
kept thinking someone was tailing me.

360
00:18:40,710 --> 00:18:42,710
I did not expect it to be you.

361
00:18:43,910 --> 00:18:45,229
What did you capture?

362
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:46,279
I did not capture anything.

363
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,039
Give me back my phone.

364
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:48,839
Password.

365
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:50,909
Why should I tell you my password?

366
00:18:50,910 --> 00:18:52,389
Besides, if you have done nothing wrong,

367
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,519
what are you afraid of?

368
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:54,319
Ma'am, listen,

369
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:55,600
he is actually a jerk.

370
00:18:56,320 --> 00:18:57,469
You are hurting me!

371
00:18:57,470 --> 00:18:59,799
You followed me and secretly filmed me.

372
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,039
That is a violation of my privacy,

373
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:01,909
do you understand?

374
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:03,389
Hurry up, the password.

375
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:05,079
If you keep this up,
I will call for help.

376
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:05,799
Go ahead.

377
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:06,629
Help! Someone!

378
00:19:06,630 --> 00:19:09,920
- Help!
- Help!

379
00:19:10,630 --> 00:19:11,920
Are you crazy?

380
00:19:12,390 --> 00:19:13,799
No one is around here.

381
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:15,839
It is secluded, so no one will come.

382
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:16,669
Tell me the password.

383
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:18,799
I will delete everything and let you go.

384
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,039
I am not telling you.

385
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,360
Not telling me, huh?

386
00:19:23,670 --> 00:19:25,790
Fine, I will tell you.

387
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,750
Five eight one two.

388
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:32,030
Five eight one two.

389
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,429
Two.

390
00:19:35,430 --> 00:19:36,550
Two.

391
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,270
What else?

392
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:42,510
Zero.

393
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:44,440
It is unlocked.

394
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:48,470
Wow,

395
00:19:48,950 --> 00:19:50,470
you took quite a lot.

396
00:19:50,910 --> 00:19:52,120
Select all.

397
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:56,160
Qian Guixiang!

398
00:19:56,950 --> 00:19:58,270
Stop right there.

399
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:02,310
Stop.

400
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:04,120
Stop.

401
00:20:12,430 --> 00:20:13,750
Stop.

402
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:18,120
Xiuguang!

403
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:44,840
Are you okay?

404
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:48,360
Help me.

405
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:55,080
Where did she go?

406
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:58,119
Did she run out?

407
00:20:58,120 --> 00:20:59,429
Impossible.

408
00:20:59,430 --> 00:21:00,750
Not that fast.

409
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,230
Look at you,

410
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:06,840
why could you not hold
your phone properly?

411
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:09,710
No, when the girl shouted,

412
00:21:10,280 --> 00:21:11,310
well,

413
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:13,709
you did not turn around, so I...

414
00:21:13,710 --> 00:21:16,119
Why did you turn around
as soon as she spoke?

415
00:21:16,120 --> 00:21:17,440
Was I not also...

416
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:20,840
Just now,

417
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,750
she said something about Qian and Xiang.

418
00:21:22,910 --> 00:21:24,270
Who is that?

419
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:26,080
Qian...

420
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:27,840
Stop.

421
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:30,079
You explain this to me.

422
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:31,510
Explain it clearly.

423
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,710
He Xiuguang, you stop right there.

424
00:21:40,990 --> 00:21:42,160
Here.

425
00:21:46,360 --> 00:21:47,840
I am sorry.

426
00:21:48,230 --> 00:21:49,279
Why are you here?

427
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,270
I was taking a walk here with my family.

428
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:52,310
What happened?

429
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:53,429
I just secretly recorded

430
00:21:53,430 --> 00:21:55,600
He Xiuguang fooling
around here with a woman.

431
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:56,879
He tried to snatch my phone

432
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,389
to delete the videos inside.

433
00:21:58,390 --> 00:21:59,469
Luckily, you were here

434
00:21:59,470 --> 00:22:00,950
and helped cover for me.

435
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:03,470
We worked together quite well.

436
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:04,950
You owe me a favor.

437
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:07,600
Is this not your case too?

438
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,909
The Sunshine Community
Elderly Care Service Center

439
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:18,119
has officially launched,

440
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:21,710
creating a one-stop new home
for happy senior living.

441
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:22,599
This morning,

442
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:24,519
the highly anticipated
Sunshine Community

443
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,799
Elderly Care Service Center

444
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:27,949
held a grand opening ceremony.

445
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:30,119
Zhang Min, Director
of the Civil Affairs Bureau,

446
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:32,469
Zhang Qiang, Director of the
Subdistrict Office, and other leaders

447
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:34,629
attended the ceremony
and cut the ribbon.

448
00:22:34,630 --> 00:22:37,149
Representatives of nearby
residents and elderly citizens

449
00:22:37,150 --> 00:22:40,030
witnessed this important
moment together.

450
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:41,640
(Sunshine Community)
Help me.

451
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,990
Xiezhi, have some Hami melon.

452
00:23:01,600 --> 00:23:03,319
I think I should move back.

453
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,550
I have to get up early tomorrow.

454
00:23:06,710 --> 00:23:07,950
What?

455
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:28,839
Why are you reading

456
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:30,920
those old, cheesy romance novels again?

457
00:23:31,630 --> 00:23:33,279
You were the one
who recommended them to me.

458
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:35,680
Back then, you even said
they had progressive views on love.

459
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:37,470
And now you are calling them cheesy.

460
00:23:39,230 --> 00:23:41,360
Do not push the blame onto me.

461
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:45,229
These days, you spend all day
either reciting sentimental poetry

462
00:23:45,230 --> 00:23:47,080
or reading cheesy romance novels.

463
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:49,120
Go on,

464
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:51,600
what new plot twist have you got?

465
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:57,879
Really?

466
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,990
Just accept it?

467
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:01,310
Accept what?

468
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,950
We are bound to separate anyway.

469
00:24:05,670 --> 00:24:07,160
Why even start?

470
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:08,990
There is no point.

471
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:11,360
Then you should tell him sooner
rather than later,

472
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:14,790
that you two should never
see each other again. Be decisive.

473
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:22,710
(Rather than breaking up indecisively,)

474
00:24:22,760 --> 00:24:25,750
(staying entangled and unable to let go)

475
00:24:25,990 --> 00:24:28,230
(it is better
to carry the relationship through,)

476
00:24:28,430 --> 00:24:30,680
(at least there will be an end one day.)

477
00:24:33,710 --> 00:24:34,880
Welcome back.

478
00:24:35,430 --> 00:24:37,400
Why are you still awake, still busy?

479
00:24:37,670 --> 00:24:38,920
I was waiting for you.

480
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:45,230
Fei is asleep?

481
00:24:47,190 --> 00:24:48,920
Why are you back so late?

482
00:24:49,230 --> 00:24:50,510
Do not even mention it.

483
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:57,079
A group came to the shop today
for team building,

484
00:24:57,080 --> 00:24:59,429
a whole crowd of people, singing and dancing,

485
00:24:59,430 --> 00:25:00,799
and they drank several cases of alcohol.

486
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:02,230
No matter how we tried,
they would not leave.

487
00:25:03,910 --> 00:25:06,120
Just take it easy with the shop.

488
00:25:06,470 --> 00:25:07,920
Your health matters most.

489
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,669
More customers

490
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:10,669
mean better business.

491
00:25:10,670 --> 00:25:12,030
Is that not a good thing?

492
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,629
Come here.

493
00:25:13,630 --> 00:25:14,840
What is it?

494
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:16,360
Take a look.

495
00:25:16,390 --> 00:25:17,949
Are these two books professional enough?

496
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:18,679
(Selected Effective Defense Documents
and Practical Guide)

497
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,469
(Commentary on Real Estate
Dispute Cases)

498
00:25:19,470 --> 00:25:20,750
They look quite professional.

499
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:22,680
What is it?

500
00:25:23,470 --> 00:25:24,909
The other day, Yu Le said

501
00:25:24,910 --> 00:25:26,149
she has a classmate

502
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:28,270
who works
as a legal director at a company.

503
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:31,319
It just so happens one of their subsidiaries
is short of a legal manager.

504
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:33,080
I think you are quite suitable.

505
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:35,710
You want me to be a legal manager?

506
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:39,119
Now that Fei is doing better,

507
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:41,600
it is time for you
to return to the legal field.

508
00:25:41,670 --> 00:25:44,839
But going back to the court
is not very suitable,

509
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:46,629
and being a lawyer in Qingcheng

510
00:25:46,630 --> 00:25:48,120
would conflict with me.

511
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,669
So being a legal manager

512
00:25:50,670 --> 00:25:52,879
is the most suitable. What do you think?

513
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,319
Come on.

514
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:56,840
I have been away for so long.

515
00:25:56,950 --> 00:25:58,359
I think things are pretty good now,

516
00:25:58,360 --> 00:25:59,840
free and easy.

517
00:25:59,910 --> 00:26:01,759
If anything happens with Fei,

518
00:26:01,760 --> 00:26:03,799
I can always make time.

519
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:06,519
You do not understand.
Once a legal manager gets busy,

520
00:26:06,520 --> 00:26:09,360
there is no way to guarantee your time.

521
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:11,709
Fei is not that clingy anymore.

522
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:13,759
Besides, since Yu Le brought it up,

523
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,230
you should just give it a try.

524
00:26:15,390 --> 00:26:17,149
So you just want me to try it,

525
00:26:17,150 --> 00:26:19,119
taking a shot in the dark?

526
00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:20,360
Is that what you mean?

527
00:26:20,630 --> 00:26:23,470
Your ability
is definitely not a problem.

528
00:26:23,670 --> 00:26:24,839
The battle has not even started yet,

529
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:26,799
why are you already discouraged?

530
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:28,229
Let me add two more books for you.

531
00:26:28,230 --> 00:26:29,189
No...

532
00:26:29,190 --> 00:26:30,709
I have not even agreed yet.

533
00:26:30,710 --> 00:26:31,949
Why are you still buying?

534
00:26:31,950 --> 00:26:34,030
There are so many books
at home that I have not finished.

535
00:26:34,470 --> 00:26:35,400
- No way.
- Do not buy them.

536
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:47,560
(Shen Xiezhi)

537
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:55,359
Hello.

538
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:57,160
Have the selection results come out?

539
00:26:57,710 --> 00:26:59,080
Xiezhi,

540
00:26:59,150 --> 00:27:00,079
each unit

541
00:27:00,080 --> 00:27:02,389
has a different review timeline.

542
00:27:02,390 --> 00:27:04,669
How would I know?
I am not the one in charge.

543
00:27:04,670 --> 00:27:06,920
Do you not have any news at all?

544
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:18,310
Do you really think
you are a legal genius,

545
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,360
passing every exam you take?

546
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:23,880
If you still have not heard
anything by now,

547
00:27:25,190 --> 00:27:26,750
there is a high chance you are out.

548
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:30,710
What?

549
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:32,200
Feeling down?

550
00:27:33,230 --> 00:27:34,359
Let me tell you,

551
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:36,080
the candidates this time

552
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:37,920
are all exceptionally strong.

553
00:27:38,670 --> 00:27:40,359
Some have received commendations,

554
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,440
and some have

555
00:27:42,990 --> 00:27:44,510
over a decade more experience than you.

556
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:46,879
It does not look promising.
Just wait for the notice.

557
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,200
It is fine.

558
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:49,950
Life is long.

559
00:27:50,470 --> 00:27:51,790
Take it slowly.

560
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:54,880
What do you mean?

561
00:27:55,670 --> 00:27:56,599
Time for bed.

562
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:57,880
Good night.

563
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:04,360
(Life is long?)

564
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:06,880
(He was acting strange again
in the middle of the night.)

565
00:28:13,470 --> 00:28:15,200
Come on, time to order.

566
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,840
I will go first. Coconut latte.

567
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:18,319
Same for me.

568
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:19,799
I will have a coconut latte too.

569
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:20,759
Same for me.

570
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,510
I will have a coconut latte too.

571
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,319
Same for me.

572
00:28:24,320 --> 00:28:25,760
- Same for me.
- Then I will have the same.

573
00:28:26,150 --> 00:28:27,189
Wait.

574
00:28:27,190 --> 00:28:28,669
I will switch to

575
00:28:28,670 --> 00:28:30,840
brown sugar stewed pear.

576
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:32,149
Hot.

577
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:33,149
Oh my god.

578
00:28:33,150 --> 00:28:35,030
Le is drinking something hot too.

579
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:37,759
Exactly. Someone who never avoids cold drinks
even during that time of the month.

580
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:38,629
Le,

581
00:28:38,630 --> 00:28:40,119
we always thought

582
00:28:40,120 --> 00:28:41,990
you would need to sleep at night

583
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:44,200
on that cold jade bed
from an ancient tomb.

584
00:28:45,710 --> 00:28:47,470
Pears are cold, right?

585
00:28:47,950 --> 00:28:49,270
They are.

586
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:51,079
Then I will switch to

587
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:53,280
red date, longan, and lotus seed soup.

588
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:55,200
What are you doing, are you
trying to protect a pregnancy?

589
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,079
Come on.

590
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:57,880
If anyone were protecting a pregnancy,
it would not be her.

591
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,519
Exactly.

592
00:28:58,520 --> 00:29:00,229
She has never missed a good cold drink.

593
00:29:00,230 --> 00:29:01,229
Do you all agree?

594
00:29:01,230 --> 00:29:02,840
- Yes.
- I think so too.

595
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:05,119
Only Judge Shen is left.

596
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:06,470
Judge Shen, what are you ordering?

597
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:08,080
Judge Shen.

598
00:29:09,990 --> 00:29:11,200
Same for me.

599
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:13,510
Same of what?

600
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,469
Judge Shen,

601
00:29:14,470 --> 00:29:16,510
your reaction is way too slow.

602
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:19,319
I will have the same as Le.

603
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,160
What, are you protecting
a pregnancy too?

604
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:23,389
What do you mean?

605
00:29:23,390 --> 00:29:24,519
So everything we just said,

606
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:26,230
you did not hear any of it?

607
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:28,470
What were you daydreaming about?

608
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:30,079
Look at Le,

609
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:31,640
she is zoning out too.

610
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,160
Le.

611
00:29:33,560 --> 00:29:35,039
What is going on

612
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:36,790
with you two today?

613
00:29:37,150 --> 00:29:39,189
Good thing we all know each other well.

614
00:29:39,190 --> 00:29:41,839
Otherwise, people might think you and Le

615
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:43,310
have something going on.

616
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,799
Alright, stop it.

617
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:47,680
Look, Judge Shen
is not even talking anymore.

618
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:49,510
I have something to do.

619
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:51,030
You all carry on.

620
00:29:51,710 --> 00:29:53,640
You aren't going to report it, right?

621
00:29:57,240 --> 00:30:02,960
(Office. Meeting Room. Changing Room)

622
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,000
Hello.

623
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:10,120
Have you finished your call?

624
00:30:10,150 --> 00:30:11,640
When is the interview?

625
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:14,080
There is no interview.

626
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,640
Why?

627
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:20,039
HR already said

628
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:22,389
this job requires
frequent business trips.

629
00:30:22,390 --> 00:30:24,840
I do not think it is suitable.

630
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:27,200
Then you should go talk
to them in person.

631
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,359
They made it very clear

632
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:29,990
on the phone.

633
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:30,669
That means

634
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:32,799
this is a serious issue.

635
00:30:32,800 --> 00:30:34,599
Why did you not discuss it with me?

636
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:36,880
How do you know
I cannot accommodate you?

637
00:30:38,390 --> 00:30:41,400
What is there to discuss
about something like this?

638
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:43,629
Forget it. You get back to work.

639
00:30:43,630 --> 00:30:44,880
I will think about it.

640
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:14,760
(Lian Yongjiu Interview)

641
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:30,120
(Qin Rui)

642
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:50,920
(Courtroom 1 Hearing in progress)
This case is transferred

643
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,480
from summary procedure
to ordinary procedure.

644
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,629
(Hearing in progress)
It will now be heard by a collegial panel.

645
00:31:54,630 --> 00:31:56,160
All rise.

646
00:31:58,190 --> 00:31:59,429
Presiding Judge,

647
00:31:59,430 --> 00:32:01,230
people's jurors, please enter.

648
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:11,160
(Qin Rui did not come?)

649
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,080
Please be seated.

650
00:32:21,150 --> 00:32:22,149
Court is now in session.

651
00:32:22,150 --> 00:32:23,680
(Hearing in progress)

652
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:24,709
Judge Shen,

653
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:25,799
sorry,

654
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:27,310
Ms. Qin could not make it.

655
00:32:27,950 --> 00:32:29,469
With the consent of the party,

656
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:30,189
I have already

657
00:32:30,190 --> 00:32:32,360
submitted the authorization letter
to the court clerk, Mr. Chen.

658
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,680
(Change of Attorney
Authorization Agreement)

659
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:40,520
(Qin Rui)

660
00:32:41,360 --> 00:32:42,920
(What is going on?)

661
00:32:43,150 --> 00:32:45,230
(Is she deliberately avoiding me?)

662
00:33:08,230 --> 00:33:09,990
Few people can truly understand,

663
00:33:10,630 --> 00:33:12,680
and I am afraid
others will say I am pretentious.

664
00:33:12,990 --> 00:33:14,230
Xiuguang,

665
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:15,669
do not do this.

666
00:33:15,670 --> 00:33:17,230
Do not do this.

667
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:18,640
Do not do this.

668
00:33:20,560 --> 00:33:21,950
I am sorry.

669
00:33:22,430 --> 00:33:23,680
No.

670
00:33:24,190 --> 00:33:25,959
I am the one who should apologize.

671
00:33:28,280 --> 00:33:29,750
Ms. Xie Yongxu

672
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:33,080
comes from a scholarly family,
dignified in character,

673
00:33:33,150 --> 00:33:34,400
kind at heart.

674
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:36,790
She became the third party passively.

675
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,839
She is willing

676
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:39,680
to appear in court
at any time for confrontation.

677
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:42,709
What else do you have to say?

678
00:33:42,710 --> 00:33:43,920
You all...

679
00:33:45,360 --> 00:33:46,950
Xiuguang, how...

680
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:49,270
how could you?

681
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:51,750
That is right.

682
00:33:52,470 --> 00:33:53,550
It was me.

683
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:56,120
Guixiang,

684
00:33:56,470 --> 00:33:57,790
I am tired.

685
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,790
I will not explain anymore.

686
00:34:00,710 --> 00:34:01,950
Let us break up.

687
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,550
In this lifetime,

688
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:07,680
I am destined to wander.

689
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:10,200
My heart, like my footsteps,

690
00:34:10,910 --> 00:34:13,359
will not stop for any woman.

691
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,469
No,

692
00:34:14,470 --> 00:34:15,949
you are lying to me.

693
00:34:15,950 --> 00:34:18,200
That is not what you used to say.

694
00:34:18,390 --> 00:34:20,230
Why

695
00:34:21,070 --> 00:34:23,029
are you so stubborn?

696
00:34:23,030 --> 00:34:25,989
Do you still not understand even now?

697
00:34:25,990 --> 00:34:28,600
From beginning to end,
I was only after your money.

698
00:34:28,910 --> 00:34:30,600
Being with someone like you,

699
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,710
a woman 23 years older than me,

700
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:34,120
what else could I want?

701
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,870
No...

702
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:38,239
You are lying to me.
I do not believe it. I do not.

703
00:34:38,240 --> 00:34:39,799
I came here today

704
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:42,200
to make a clean break with you.

705
00:34:42,550 --> 00:34:43,910
I am done speaking.

706
00:34:44,990 --> 00:34:47,160
Your Honor, may I be excused?

707
00:34:47,990 --> 00:34:49,230
No,

708
00:34:49,240 --> 00:34:50,639
you are not allowed to leave.

709
00:34:50,640 --> 00:34:53,310
No one can take you away from me.

710
00:34:53,910 --> 00:34:55,759
Are you trying to drive me to death?

711
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,759
I raised you all for nothing.

712
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,230
If he leaves,

713
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,319
I will not go on living.

714
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,480
Mom!

715
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,710
Xiuguang,

716
00:35:05,390 --> 00:35:06,759
do not leave.

717
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,960
I know you are lying to me.

718
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,680
You have no choice.

719
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:14,600
You are putting on an act for them.

720
00:35:14,910 --> 00:35:17,960
You do not want us
to turn against each other.

721
00:35:18,390 --> 00:35:21,230
You do not want me
to be caught in the middle.

722
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,639
You have nothing to do with that woman,

723
00:35:23,640 --> 00:35:24,910
right?

724
00:35:26,990 --> 00:35:28,310
You are not allowed to leave.

725
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,710
I will not let you go.

726
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:31,040
My life

727
00:35:31,110 --> 00:35:33,480
has already wasted sixty-one years.

728
00:35:33,950 --> 00:35:35,069
I do not want to waste

729
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:37,120
a single day for the remaining 20 years.

730
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,319
Judge,

731
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,799
please issue the judgment
as soon as possible.

732
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,639
Return my property to me.

733
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:43,839
I want to start a new life

734
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,680
with Mr. He right away.

735
00:35:45,990 --> 00:35:47,680
Now, immediately.

736
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,310
Xiuguang.

737
00:35:51,430 --> 00:35:52,750
Guixiang.

738
00:35:53,160 --> 00:35:54,480
Xiuguang.

739
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:56,960
Dear.

740
00:35:58,110 --> 00:35:59,759
- Mom!
- Mom,

741
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,469
are you out of your mind?

742
00:36:01,470 --> 00:36:02,429
Sit down.

743
00:36:02,430 --> 00:36:03,389
This man is a fraud.

744
00:36:03,390 --> 00:36:05,069
You should arrest him right now!

745
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:05,639
Sit down.

746
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:08,109
He Xiuguang, you shameless man,
come out here if you have the guts.

747
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:09,069
Come!

748
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,710
Sun Daming, what are you trying to do?

749
00:36:11,550 --> 00:36:12,719
Do not be afraid.

750
00:36:12,720 --> 00:36:13,759
Defendant,

751
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,120
control your emotions.

752
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:17,310
Wait for the judge's decision.

753
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:20,200
Whoever can stay calm now
will win the case.

754
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,200
Court is adjourned for deliberation.

755
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:39,389
I stand with the children.

756
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:41,750
This man is a complete fraud.

757
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,910
Exactly.

758
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:44,989
He specifically targets
elderly women lacking affection.

759
00:36:44,990 --> 00:36:47,069
This house cannot be awarded
to Qian Guixiang.

760
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,239
If you award it to her,

761
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:50,159
He Xiuguang will cheat her out of it.

762
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:52,429
By then, she will lose both her money
and everything else.

763
00:36:52,430 --> 00:36:54,199
If her children get angry
and stop caring for her,

764
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:55,680
how will she live?

765
00:36:56,390 --> 00:36:57,960
I do not understand the law very well,

766
00:36:58,470 --> 00:37:00,390
but is her revocation justified?

767
00:37:00,470 --> 00:37:01,469
If we can avoid supporting it,

768
00:37:01,470 --> 00:37:02,799
I do not agree to give it to her either.

769
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:04,279
From what we see now,

770
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,199
the children
are not completely unfilial.

771
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:07,469
If the property stays with them,

772
00:37:07,470 --> 00:37:09,069
He Xiuguang will not gain anything

773
00:37:09,070 --> 00:37:10,640
and will back off on his own.

774
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:11,719
Just now, I felt

775
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,429
that he was already
looking for a way out.

776
00:37:13,430 --> 00:37:14,679
I just did not expect the elderly lady

777
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:16,080
to be so stubborn.

778
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:17,639
I think

779
00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:19,390
he is not someone who gives up easily.

780
00:37:19,470 --> 00:37:20,710
What he is doing

781
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:22,120
is playing hard to get.

782
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:26,199
Otherwise,

783
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,989
we could follow that lawyer's suggestion

784
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,390
and bring that woman in to testify.

785
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:33,200
The other party
has some social standing.

786
00:37:33,430 --> 00:37:35,270
She may not be willing to testify.

787
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,359
And just now, He Xiuguang

788
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,270
has already blocked that path.

789
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:40,600
Even if she does testify,

790
00:37:41,390 --> 00:37:42,759
the plaintiff
might still convince herself

791
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,909
that it is all staged,

792
00:37:43,910 --> 00:37:45,310
that she was hired.

793
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:47,109
Then it seems

794
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:48,480
this is a dead end.

795
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,080
(Application for Property Preservation)

796
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:53,920
(Lefu Dog Farm)

797
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:58,799
Is the dog farm owned
by Sun Daming and his sister

798
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:01,830
near Qingshan Lake Wetland Park?

799
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:03,549
I remember there

800
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:05,509
is a retirement apartment nearby.

801
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:07,350
I think I saw news before

802
00:38:07,390 --> 00:38:08,759
that the project was stalled.

803
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,429
Xinglang Real Estate took it over later.

804
00:38:10,430 --> 00:38:11,989
Now the first phase is already occupied.

805
00:38:11,990 --> 00:38:13,509
My mom went to see it with a friend.

806
00:38:13,510 --> 00:38:15,350
They said the conditions are quite good.

807
00:38:15,950 --> 00:38:18,310
Away from the hustle,
a place to rest and recuperate.

808
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:21,350
The cafeteria provides three meals a day,
and even late-night snacks.

809
00:38:21,430 --> 00:38:23,199
They say the food is quite good too.

810
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:25,790
And the community hospital is open 24/7.

811
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,910
It sounds like a good retirement option.

812
00:38:27,990 --> 00:38:29,230
It is just...

813
00:38:29,910 --> 00:38:30,909
Just what?

814
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:32,109
Too quiet.

815
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,199
Absolutely quiet.

816
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:36,230
Aside from the retirement home
and nearby villagers, no one goes there.

817
00:38:36,910 --> 00:38:39,199
Is that not exactly
what retirement needs, a quiet place?

818
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:41,750
Beautiful mountains,
good water, great scenery.

819
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,480
But if the body ages
while the heart does not,

820
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:46,710
then beautiful scenery
may just become boring.

821
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:50,719
(Qingcheng District People's Court)

822
00:38:50,720 --> 00:38:52,350
After deliberation,

823
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,640
before issuing a formal judgment,

824
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:55,679
the collegial panel

825
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:57,319
would like to seek
both parties' opinions.

826
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:59,159
Are you willing to accept mediation?

827
00:38:59,160 --> 00:39:00,549
How would we mediate?

828
00:39:00,550 --> 00:39:02,589
The condition for the mother
to gift the property to them

829
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:04,000
was that they treat her well.

830
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:04,949
But now,

831
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:05,879
have they considered

832
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,600
her happiness at all?

833
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,230
Qian Guixiang, what do you think?

834
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:13,120
They cannot stand seeing me happy.

835
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,199
Mom,

836
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,159
if you insist on thinking that way,
I will not stop you.

837
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:17,750
I do not care what my brother thinks.

838
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,239
You can take back

839
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,480
the property under my name.

840
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:22,319
But let me be clear,

841
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:24,509
if you suffer losses in the future
and are left with nothing,

842
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:26,000
do not come crying to me.

843
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,279
Mom,

844
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,680
think this through.

845
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:32,429
Both sides, please calm down.

846
00:39:32,430 --> 00:39:34,069
After several discussions in court,

847
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,350
I believe

848
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:36,589
there is no

849
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:38,910
irreconcilable conflict between you.

850
00:39:38,990 --> 00:39:39,989
The mother

851
00:39:39,990 --> 00:39:42,639
seeks freedom
in her later-life marriage,

852
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:43,239
while the children

853
00:39:43,240 --> 00:39:45,480
are concerned
about her property security.

854
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:48,710
They are not trying
to take her rental income.

855
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,109
The core issue

856
00:39:50,110 --> 00:39:51,520
lies in

857
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:54,200
your trust in the mother's partner.

858
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,080
Based on this,

859
00:39:56,240 --> 00:39:57,710
the court hopes

860
00:39:57,800 --> 00:40:00,710
to find a solution
acceptable to everyone

861
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:03,160
without harming your relationship.

862
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,759
I have a proposal.

863
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:07,000
See if you are willing to accept it.

864
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:08,839
Your mother's health

865
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,310
has not been very good.

866
00:40:10,470 --> 00:40:12,719
And the children are busy with work,

867
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:14,790
unable to stay by her side.

868
00:40:15,110 --> 00:40:17,790
Mr. He can stay with her,

869
00:40:18,030 --> 00:40:21,159
providing emotional support

870
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,199
and taking care

871
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:24,350
of her daily needs.

872
00:40:24,950 --> 00:40:25,989
I believe

873
00:40:25,990 --> 00:40:28,040
you should accept him

874
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:29,680
as you would a family member.

875
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:32,160
Judge Shen, you see things clearly.

876
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:39,839
Defendants,

877
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:41,520
are you willing

878
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:43,109
to have the two plaintiffs

879
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:46,080
move into your dog farm?

880
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:51,830
No, no need for that trouble.

881
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:54,159
Guixiang and I
are fine living in the city.

882
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:55,719
We are free and easy.

883
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,000
We are not troubling anyone.

884
00:40:57,070 --> 00:40:58,909
Besides, Guixiang's health
is not very good,

885
00:40:58,910 --> 00:41:00,600
she needs to go to the hospital often.

886
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:01,799
No need to trouble.

887
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,389
The dog farm
and Qingshan Lake Wetland Park

888
00:41:03,390 --> 00:41:04,870
are separated by just a river,

889
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:07,390
adjacent to
Taiyang City Retirement Apartments.

890
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:08,989
The facilities are complete,

891
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:10,560
and the medical conditions
are excellent,

892
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:13,230
especially in elderly care.

893
00:41:14,990 --> 00:41:17,160
This arrangement is beneficial for us.

894
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:20,160
He says this is beneficial for us.

895
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,319
Of course,

896
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:24,120
if Mr. He is afraid of loneliness,

897
00:41:24,240 --> 00:41:25,750
that is another matter.

898
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,040
No...

899
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:32,910
I think Judge Shen's suggestion is good.

900
00:41:34,430 --> 00:41:35,639
You,

901
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:38,359
move to the dog farm

902
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,870
with my mom.

903
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,879
We have long thought

904
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:43,509
that since my mom is getting older,

905
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:44,960
we should live together.

906
00:41:45,070 --> 00:41:46,589
It is just that the dog farm

907
00:41:46,590 --> 00:41:48,120
is too remote,

908
00:41:48,160 --> 00:41:50,710
no one to chat with her,
we worry she will feel lonely.

909
00:41:50,910 --> 00:41:52,480
Now that you are there,

910
00:41:52,950 --> 00:41:55,160
we can focus on our own work,

911
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:57,160
and you can stay with my mom,

912
00:41:57,390 --> 00:41:59,870
take walks here and there.

913
00:42:00,590 --> 00:42:02,000
Thirty mu of the dog farm

914
00:42:02,240 --> 00:42:04,029
and two thousand mu of the wetland park

915
00:42:04,030 --> 00:42:05,710
are all your private garden.

916
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:08,310
You two can enjoy

917
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,719
your later years there.

918
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:10,879
No, we...

919
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:12,710
We should discuss this further.

920
00:42:13,640 --> 00:42:15,120
This old scoundrel

921
00:42:15,200 --> 00:42:17,560
will not be able
to stay at the dog farm.

922
00:42:18,470 --> 00:42:20,270
What is yours will remain yours.

923
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:25,639
Guixiang, let us discuss this.

924
00:42:25,640 --> 00:42:26,469
About where to live...

925
00:42:26,470 --> 00:42:28,270
We will go.

926
00:42:29,470 --> 00:42:31,640
The children have finally accepted you.

927
00:42:32,470 --> 00:42:33,389
Thank you.

928
00:42:33,390 --> 00:42:35,750
Thank you, Judge Shen. Thank you.

929
00:42:42,840 --> 00:42:45,840
(Office)

930
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

931
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

932
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

933
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

934
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

935
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

936
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

937
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

938
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

939
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

940
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

941
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

942
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

943
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

944
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

945
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

946
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

947
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

948
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

949
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

950
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

951
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

952
